<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h5>I'm Thuy Oanh or you can call me Jient</h5>
        <h6>My hobbies are reading books, traveling, coding.</h6></br>
      
        <p>>>NANer || NAKer || NHCer || HCMUPer >></br>

          ______________________________________________________ </br>

 
          >> Programmer >> Photographer >> Dreamer >> </br>

          ______________________________________________________ </br>
      
          >> Change what you can and accept what you cannot!!! >></p></br>
           
          <h6>Favorite Quotes: </h6>
          <p>“It seems that the more places I see and experience, 
          the bigger I realize the world to be. 
          The more I become aware of,
          the more I realize how relatively little I know of it,
          how many places I have still to go, 
          how much more there is to learn. 
          Maybe that’s enlightenment enough – to know
          that there is no final resting place of the mind,
          no moment of smug clarity. Perhaps wisdom, at least for me,
          means realizing how small I am, and unwise, and how far I have yet to go.” </br>
          - Anthony Bourdain - </p></br>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
          
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#certificate"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="certificate"
          >
            Certifications
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              None!
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row col-md-8">
                <div class="col-md-2 info-img">
                  <%= image_tag "logo1.png", width: 60, alt: "profile image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-10 info">
                  <h6> Ho Chi Minh city University of Education</h6>
                  <p>Bachelor's degree, Computer science Teacher Education</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row col-md-8">
                <div class="col-md-2 info-img">
                  <%= image_tag "logo2.png", width: 60, alt: "profile image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-10 info">
                  <h6> Korea Advanced Institute of Science and Technology</h6>
                  <p>Associate's Degree, Cloud Computing</p>
                  <p>The 2nd ICT / SW Experts Training Program</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="collapse" id="certificate">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row col-md-8">
                <div class="col-md-2 info-img">
                  <%= image_tag "logo2.png", width: 60, alt: "profile image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-10 info">
                  <h6>Certification of Completion of the ICT / SW Experts Training Program</h6>
                  <p>Korea Advanced Institute of Science and Technology, License 16-0059</p>
                  <em>June 2016 - Today</em>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row col-md-8">
                <div class="col-md-2 info-img">
                  <%= image_tag "logo4.jpg", width: 60, alt: "profile image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-10 info">
                  <h6>Certification of Completion of the Ruby on Rails 5 Training Course</h6>
                  <p>Jordan Hudgens & Udemy , License UC-6JQ9O8H7</p>
                  <em>July 2018 - Today</em>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>          
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>